snippet.title: Jumpstart Reading for 2nd Graders Full Walkthrough
snippet.description:
Jumpstart Reading for 2nd Graders Full Walkthrough

JumpStart Reading for Second Graders originally known as JumpStart 2nd Grade Reading is a game released in 1998 that focuses on a second grade reading curriculum.

In 1999, JumpStart Reading for Second Graders and its kindergarten and first grade counterparts were packaged and sold together as the JumpStart Learn to Read bundle.
